title: 2021 Week 16 Preview
itunes:title: 2021 Week 16 Preview
description:
A virtual room filled with some heroes - Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler and Gregg Rosenthal preview every single upcoming game of Week 16, starting with the Saturday games on Christmas Day. Then we discuss the primetime contests before getting into the draft. Come for the locks of the week, stay for the incredible holiday gift for the listeners from Dan.
